oto]] \u2022 Shinya Tanuichi <small>(rap)</small>\n| music11          = Akira Kagimoto\n| extra11          = Akira Kagimoto\n| length11         = 3:59\n\n| title12          = Ride On Music\n| note12           =\n| lyrics12         = Akira Kagimoto \u2022 Shinya Tanuichi <small>(rap)</small>\n| music12          = Akira Kagimoto \u2022 Nobuyuki Nishikawa <small>(guitar)</small>\n| extra12          = Akira Kagimoto\n| length12         = 3:24\n\n| title13          = [[Hide and Seek/Sunset Refrain|Hide and Seek]]\n| note13           =\n| lyrics13         = Akira Kagimoto \u2022 Shinya Tanuichi <small>(rap)</small>\n| music13          = MASAT \u2022 [[After Romeo|Drew Ryan Scott]]\n| extra13          = MASAT\n| length13         = 3:00\n}}\n{{tracklist\n| collapsed       = \n| headline        = Disc 2\n| extra_column    = Arranger(s)\n| total_length    = \n\n| title1          = \"Thursday Boys' Association\" SP ~Singularity Radio~\n| note1           = \u6728\u66dc\u65e5\u306e\u7537\u5b50\u4f1a\n| lyrics1         = \n| music1          = \n| extra1          = \n| length1         = \n\n| title2          = Summer Vacation\n| note2           = Lingering Summer Heat Remix) (remixed by Akira\n| lyrics2         = \n| music2          = \n| extra2          = \n| length2         = \n\n| title3          = [[Beautiful Day (Lead song)|Say Good-bye Say Hello]]\n| note3           = [[Lead Upturn 2019: Sync|Lead Upturn 2019 ~Sync~]] Live ver.\n| lyrics3         = \n| music3          = \n| extra3          = \n| length3         = \n}}\n{{tracklist\n| collapsed       = \n| headline        = DVD\n| extra_column    = Director(s)\n| total_length    =\n\n| title1          = [[Be the Naked]]\n| note1           = Music Video\n| extra1          = Takuya Tada\n| length1         = 4:07\n\n| title2          = [[Summer Vacation (song)|Summer Vacation]]\n| note2           = Music Video\n| extra2          = Takuya Tada\n| length2         = 2:57\n\n| title3          = [[Hide and Seek/Sunset Refrain|Sunset 