. All events between March 18 and March 22 were cancelled indefinitely.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ameblo.jp/lead-blog/entry-12576790697.html|title=\u3010\u30b9\u30bf\u30c3\u30d5\u3088\u308a\u30112\u670822\u65e5\uff5e3\u670822\u65e5CD\u767a\u58f2\u8a18\u5ff5\u30a4\u30d9\u30f3\u30c8\u306e\u958b\u50ac\u4e2d\u6b62\u304a\u3088\u3073\u5ef6\u671f\u306e\u304a\u77e5\u3089\u305b|work=Ameba|date=February 21, 2020|accessdate=March 17, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits are adapted from album\u2019s Liner Notes<ref>{{cite AV media notes|title=Singularity|others=[[Lead (band)|Lead]]|year=2020|url=|page=22|type=booklet|publisher=[[Pony Canyon]]|location=Japan}}</ref>\n;Musicians\n*[[Lead (band)|Shinya Tanuichi]] - vocals\n*[[Lead (band)|Keita Furuya]] - vocals\n*[[Lead (band)|Akira Kagimoto]] - vocals\n\n;Production\n*Naotaka Yamaguchi - producer\n*Shigeru Kawai - director\n*Daisuke Nishizawa - director\n*Hajime Kodama - vocal direction\n*Yoshihiro Kinoshita - coordination\n*Yukihito Sakakibara - music producer\n*Takashi Kasuga - supervisor\n*T. Taira - executive producer\n*Hideaki Hiraki - artist management\n*Takashi Tsuboi - audio and recording\n*Yoko Abe - products coordinator\n*Mayumi Nakagawa - sales promotion\n*Nobuaki Iijima - art direction\n*Misa Tsukagoshi - design\n*Susumu Miyawaki - photographer\n*Yuya Murata - stylist\n*Shunsuke Takata - hair and make-up\n*Yukio Takemura - public relation\n*Akira Kobayashi - public relation\n*Toshiyuki Yamamoto - public relation\n*Masahiko Iida - public relation\n*Motoki Mishima - public relation\n*Kotaro Sakaki - public relation\n*Koichi Tadokoro - public relation\n*Miho Watanabe - public relation\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+''Billboard Japan'' chart performance for ''Singularity''\n!align=\"left\"|Release\n!align=\"left\"|Chart\n!align=\"left\"|Peak position\n!align=\"left\"|Chart run\n!align=\"left\"|Total sales\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|March 18, 2020\n|align=\"left\"|[[Billboard Japan]]\n|align=\"center\"|15\n|align=\